Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined\Nthat this day would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I forgot\Nthat girls walk slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. No need to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.98,0:00:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make it clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...there won't be any\Nof that daily diary exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...or using a beeper business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Needless to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.27,0:00:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...there won't be any\Nmatching clothes either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.74,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And birthdays...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...Christmas, Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.16,0:01:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A FORMIDABLE FOE?!\NA MISCHIEVOUS PIXIE'S TRAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered\Nthat this is the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Mysterious Thief Lucifer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...who is Eimi Haneoka.\NSince monitoring this house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...Lucifer hasn't shown...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...any movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...but her daughter\Nsometimes goes out at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time she goes out,\Nthe next morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's an article about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.27,0:01:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look! Look at the article\Nabout St. Tail this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She escaped\Nfrom you again, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he has Meimi now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't care about St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of logic is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.34,0:02:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I will definitely catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to impress Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.25,0:02:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.39,0:02:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you jumping\Nto all of these conclusions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fortune teller.\NI've heard she is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A fortune teller?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I've heard that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a cover story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What he really wants to know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.03,0:02:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...how their relationship is going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go! Let's change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get mad!\NWe're happy for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NFinally you two got together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she choose\NAsuka over me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get away\Nfrom me, Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unusual to see you here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy! I can't even have\Na broken heart in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed, Takamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What else can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, those two took...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.27,0:03:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...too long to get together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. So half of it\Nwas stubborn pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll have\NGod's blessings, Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,God's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.34,0:04:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My beautiful face...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm hitting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I feel good.\NThat's interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So God's blessings...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...may not be necessary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,FORTUNE TELLING
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fortune teller's house\Nthat Kyoko was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't interested in this\Nkind of stuff. Let's forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask her\Nabout the location of St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.19,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go in, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just opened\Na fortune telling shop near this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come by\Nwith your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've heard your fortunes\Nare very accurate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...whether you are right\Nfor each other, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When I see you two, I can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your names and dates of birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi Haneoka,\Nborn on September 29th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And Asuka Jr. is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiki Asuka, August 12th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So he is Asuka Jr.,\Nspecial agent for the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do\Nwith the crystal ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A thick fog is\Nfilling the crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.58,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can't see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such thick fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can see a ring\Naround his finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be\Nabout the secret promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a one-sided promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is she talking\Nabout St. Tail and Asuka Jr?.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the ring can\Nnever be removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,His character\Nand straightforwardness...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...is indicated in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, this relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...is doomed to failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding something\Nvery big from him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've hit the bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I hate\Nfortune telling stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She knew things\Nwithout getting any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who talk\Nnonsense and tell lies...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...are the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Unremovable ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then.\NLet's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...that he can't forgive\Npeople who deceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he won't forgive\Nmy being St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.53,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, a person\Nnamed Sakiko visited here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She valued it a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know about Pandora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...the fortune telling place,\Ndon't you, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakiko went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My statue of Mary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That solid-gold statue of Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...is bringing you misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can bring\Nthe solid-gold statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...of Mary to us immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take full responsibility\Nfor its disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!\NHow could I...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared\Nto have misfortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So did she give it away? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose\Nthe fortune teller uses hypnosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So Sakiko can't go to the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- I went there.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to the fortune teller...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and she gave me\Na scary fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If Asuka Jr. finds out I'm St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been deceiving me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop stealing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate what you\Nhave done very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't need...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...to see Asuka Jr.\Nas St. Tail anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's end it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. I love you, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.04,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't desert those\Npeople who are in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get back\Nthe solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's lunch time!\NLunch time! Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought a lunchbox\Ntoday, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.28,0:10:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...since St. Tail\Nbooby-trapped your lunchbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'll get\Nthe solid-gold statue of Mary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy! She really\Nwent all out on this lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haneoka.\NLook at Asuka's lunchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop it!\N- Then let us eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me make lots and lots\Nof whatever you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens\Nfrom this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,COOKBOOK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...I hope I have no regrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.11,0:11:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.41,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me\Nwhen things get too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If it happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If it happens, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...will become St. Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Seira...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.20,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's made of solid gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Our store doesn't have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,SAKURAI JEWELERS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have such a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A solid-gold statue of Mary...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our store doesn't have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That St. Tail! Where is it?\NWhere is the location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world is there\Na solid-gold statue of Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious Thief St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you here...\Nwhere she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get\Nthe statue of Mary back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here.\NThat's what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have several things\NI want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't this smell nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This fragrance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell in a bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lavender!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your date of birth?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,September...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...29th...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your father's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Genichiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...the daughter\Nof the Mysterious Thief Lucifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Meimi Haneoka,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are\Nthe Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi Haneoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.01,0:15:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.80,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hiding it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared that you'd find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.33,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to know your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You said some\Nunexpected things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hypnotized...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have my secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...revealed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able\Nto continue my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Your business?\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing people's valuables?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not planning to reveal\Nyour identity to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you what I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.23,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...taking revenge\Non the Mysterious Thief Lucifer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,On my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take the statue\Nof Mary, Ms. St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.56,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the statue of Mary!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the statue of Mary,\NMs. Fortune Teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.90,0:18:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...what will happen if she\Ncontinues with that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hypnosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Meimi Haneoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to stop her hypnosis...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, my body got cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the real Asuka Jr.\Nwas asking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The solid-gold statue\Nof Mary was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most valuable item...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...out of everything\Nwe've gotten recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maju.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer is living a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be fun to make her suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And the daughter's pain\Nis her mother's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm with you all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have\Nmore fun that way, Maju.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mysterious Thief St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle is just now starting...
